The [[Almas Academy]] maintained a presence on [[Cularin/Legends|Cularin]] with a small '''Jedi enclave''' located in the northeast corner of [[Gadrin]]. It was a satellite facility for the Academy, not being at all like the ancient [[Jedi Enclaves]]. When [[E1-6RA]] recruited a group to look into the disappearances of people around Gadrin and Hedrett, she had them meet her there.<ref name="trw">{{LivingForce|Eye of the Sun: The Resistance Within}}</ref>

With the start of the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] and a blockade by [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]] [[Darrus Jeht/Legends|Darrus Jeht]] on the Almas Academy, the facility held the classes that could not take place on Almas.

